snippet.title: The Asteroid Mines
snippet.description: A quick playthrough of the Asteroid Mines, the level available to play in the Sector Alpha demo. It's a freeflight type of level where the player is tasked with destroying incoming missiles threatening to detonate a much larger, very volatile substance within a nearby cargo ship.
